FIELD OBSERVATIONS: Our two examples of 
<taxonomicName box="[128,454,1036,1059]" class="Mammalia" family="Phyllostomidae" genus="Micronycteris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="79" pageNumber="79" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="schmidtorum">
